{"tid":733071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罕見！ 2艘美國主力神盾驅逐艦       上午由台灣南部海域航行通過台灣海峽","createTime":"2018-07-07T12:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T06:43:38.000Z","uid":35790,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ad96c7e1ea47e22e986f06fd9dfb6082a93b15b1","tid":733071,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:41:49.000Z","msg":"罕見！ 2艘美軍驅逐艦 通過台灣海峽<br />\n<br />\n2018-07-07 20:16<br />\n<br />\n〔記者涂鉅旻／台北報導〕國防部稍早表示，美國軍艦DDG-89及DDG-65兩艦上午由我國南部海域航經台灣海峽，研判續向東北航行。美艦航行期間，國軍依規定對周邊海、空情狀況全程掌握與應變處置。<br />\n<br />\n根據國防部公佈的美軍軍艦舷號，這二艘軍艦為美國主力神盾驅逐艦「伯克級」，具備優異的防空、反艦戰力，亦可搭載攻陸巡弋飛彈。<br />\n<br />\n國防部強調，國軍時刻堅守崗位，掌握周邊動態，有信心與能力維護區域穩定，捍衞國家安全。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2481377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2481377&d=WDp8gKrEpb2cwY35X3V8FXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=141a722d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2481377&h=92b537a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2481377</a>"},{"pid":"6365df583e8aaa8a43ac3306d7048a98aeb4e48f","tid":733071,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"口交部呢？"},{"pid":"20764d7178444dad9c40eb19980e267b72820192","tid":733071,"uid":71315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:45:41.000Z","msg":"國軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8384458b6d322bd3ed8e1549b46593596f125d","tid":733071,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"傳美軍艦欲過台灣海峽 華官媒：「離台海遠一點」<br />\n<br />\n2018-06-06 15:06<br />\n<br />\n有外國傳媒昨日 (5日) 報道，美國考慮派遣軍艦通過台灣海峽。消息引起中方不滿，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國官媒刊登評論，直斥「美國軍艦最好還是離台海遠一點」。</span><br />\n<br />\n《環球網》的評論質疑，美國有些人認為「美國找中國麻煩很容易，代價極低，甚至可以零代價，但有可能收獲中國對美國利益的更多配合和順從」。評論認為，「美國迄今沒能嚇唬住一個小國，怎麼可能將中國這樣的力量恐嚇住」，又指台海靠近中國，中國能調動的資源和手段也最多。最後，評論要求美軍別離台海太近，否則雙方對抗「將是美方的不可承受之重」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，美國軍艦小鷹號航母曾於2000年台灣總統大選前通過台灣海峽，及於2007年穿越台海北返日本橫須賀港。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/chi/1234218/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1234218%2F&d=WDp8gKrEpb2cwY35X3V8FXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1d3697ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/chi/1234218/</a>"},{"pid":"0560b607bcc9b9022f725a541424bc3970ab66ee","tid":733071,"uid":78143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/152731_22f88faada771373a07c0289ca8bbe7a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F152731_22f88faada771373a07c0289ca8bbe7a.gif&h=197902a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1dcd01dd1d8f4b1643babd4824459125dcc5412","tid":733071,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:51:21.000Z","msg":"Tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bc901527a560cb9653f4cae7fc5aae5280e675","tid":733071,"uid":35790,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:51:31.000Z","msg":"大陸強硬表態：美軍艦若穿台灣海峽 解放軍必讓蔡英文哭<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mwTEMqnxC0Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmwTEMqnxC0Y&d=WDp8gKrEpb2cwY35X3V8FXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f391a3ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mwTEMqnxC0Y</a>"},{"pid":"d15abeedc466810cbc42a3e02a99f2ad2a57ce0e","tid":733071,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T13:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />